parameters.name: Volume ID
parameters.description:
The volume_id element uniquely identifies a data volume.  
                                   Example: LP_0001.

parameters.name: Product ID
parameters.description:
The product_id element uniquely identifies a data product.  
                                   The product_id for a Lunar Prospector merged telemetry file 
                                   is the file name used by the LP project.

parameters.name: Start Time
parameters.description:
Start time of a telemetry data gap in UTC.  
                                   Format is yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm.

parameters.name: Stop Time
parameters.description:
Stop time of a telemetry data gap in UTC.  
                                   Format is yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm.

parameters.name: Outage Description
parameters.description:
This element describes provides information about the cause of 
                                   a telemetry data gap or outage.

parameters.name: Outage Status
parameters.description:
This element describes the action, if, any, taken to correct the 
                                   telemetry data gap or outage.
